snippet.title: VGX 2013: Broken Age Premiere Trailer
snippet.description:
Elijah Wood joins the cast of Tim Schafer's upcoming game in this behind-the-scenes reveal trailer. 

For all the excitement of VGX head over to: http://www.gametrailers.com/vgx?xrs=synd_yt_endslate
